com.igormaznitsa.prol.libraries
Class PredicateProcessor

java.lang.Object
  com.igormaznitsa.prol.libraries.PredicateProcessor

public final class PredicateProcessor
extends java.lang.Object

The auxulary inside class describes a predicate processor. It means that the processor contains all links to method and the object instance of a library which should execute the predicate.

Author:
Igor Maznitsa (igor.maznitsa@igormaznitsa.com)
See Also:
Method, ProlAbstractLibrary, PredicateTemplate
